title: Lea Anne Powell (driver, model)
description: Accomplished driver and model Lea Anne Powell joins us and we talk about karting, recording police officers, Total Recall, the future of the GTR, modding daily drivers, really bad hip-hop, and cars we've destroyed.
author: matt@thesmokingtire.com (Matt Farah & Zack Klapman)
